1
00:00:25,442 --> 00:00:26,608
[SHADOW]
Majesty...

2
00:00:26,692 --> 00:00:28,692
If I may say so,

3
00:00:28,775 --> 00:00:31,150
you don't need to make
this trip yourself.

4
00:00:31,233 --> 00:00:32,442
[MIRELIA]
The country's--

5
00:00:32,525 --> 00:00:36,108
no, the entire world's
survival is at stake.

6
00:00:36,192 --> 00:00:38,108
I will not sit here
and wait for news

7
00:00:38,192 --> 00:00:40,817
when I still have the
strength within me to fight.

8
00:00:40,900 --> 00:00:42,983
[SHADOW]
As you wish.

9
00:00:43,067 --> 00:00:44,900
I apologize for this.

10
00:00:44,983 --> 00:00:46,192
Not at all.

11
00:00:46,275 --> 00:00:48,858
Your Majesty, we live for this.

12
00:00:59,358 --> 00:01:02,567
[SOLDIERS gasping]

13
00:01:06,567 --> 00:01:08,400
Today we go to war!

14
00:01:08,483 --> 00:01:10,858
Pope Bisca T. Balmus
is a traitor.

15
00:01:10,942 --> 00:01:13,442
It's time to put an end
to the Three Heroes Church

16
00:01:13,525 --> 00:01:14,775
and its followers.

17
00:01:14,858 --> 00:01:16,150
[SOLDIERS]
Right!

18
00:01:16,233 --> 00:01:17,817
We leave immediately!

19
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:19,525
Cavalry, move out!

20
00:01:19,608 --> 00:01:23,233
--[horses neigh]
--[SOLDIERS cheer]

21
00:01:23,317 --> 00:01:25,525
Shield Hero, please
survive till I get there.

22
00:01:25,608 --> 00:01:27,817
Our troops will be there soon.

23
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,317
Hang on, Melty.

24
00:01:47,317 --> 00:01:50,650
And now for group defense
magic of the highest level:

25
00:01:50,733 --> 00:01:52,775
Cathedral!

26
00:01:52,858 --> 00:01:58,858
[bell tolls]

27
00:02:24,983 --> 00:02:26,525
[REN]
Thunderbolt Slash!

28
00:02:26,608 --> 00:02:28,150
Thunder Shot!

29
00:02:33,275 --> 00:02:34,817
Filo! Raphtalia!

30
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,400
--Right!
--[FILO] 'Kay!

31
00:02:40,525 --> 00:02:42,233
[FILO]
High Quick!

32
00:02:45,275 --> 00:02:47,150
[RAPHTALIA yells]

33
00:02:47,233 --> 00:02:48,192
[RAPHTALIA grunts]

34
00:02:49,483 --> 00:02:51,442
[POPE groans]

35
00:02:51,525 --> 00:02:53,150
[CLERGY praying]

36
00:02:53,233 --> 00:02:55,025
[PRIEST 19A]
Heal my target!

37
00:02:55,108 --> 00:02:57,275
Zweit Heal!

38
00:03:03,442 --> 00:03:04,525
Filo!

39
00:03:04,608 --> 00:03:05,442
One more time.

40
00:03:05,525 --> 00:03:06,692
'Kay!

41
00:03:06,775 --> 00:03:07,817
Grab him, too!

42
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,025
Huh? [screams]

43
00:03:10,108 --> 00:03:11,567
Wait a sec!

44
00:03:11,650 --> 00:03:14,025
Zweit Aqua Shell!

45
00:03:14,108 --> 00:03:16,067
[MYNE gasps]

46
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:17,275
[ALL gasp]

47
00:03:17,358 --> 00:03:19,942
Come on, Sister,
keep your focus!

48
00:03:20,025 --> 00:03:21,900
[NAOFUMI] Okay, Motoyasu,
when we get close

49
00:03:21,983 --> 00:03:23,650
I want you to attack me, got it?

50
00:03:23,733 --> 00:03:25,608
Huh?! But why?!

51
00:03:25,692 --> 00:03:26,525
[FILO grunts]

52
00:03:26,608 --> 00:03:28,733
[MOTOYASU screams]

53
00:03:28,817 --> 00:03:29,900
[NAOFUMI]
Now!

54
00:03:29,983 --> 00:03:32,483
Fine, then! [grunts]

55
00:03:34,275 --> 00:03:37,733
[yells]

56
00:03:47,942 --> 00:03:50,400
He dispelled that
curse so easily.

57
00:03:50,483 --> 00:03:51,942
[POPE]
All curses are meaningless

58
00:03:52,025 --> 00:03:53,900
within the walls
of this Cathedral.

59
00:03:53,983 --> 00:03:56,900
After all, we are standing
on hallowed ground

60
00:03:56,983 --> 00:03:59,525
that has been blessed
by God himself.

61
00:04:01,817 --> 00:04:03,442
[BOTH grunt]

62
00:04:03,525 --> 00:04:04,275
[NAOFUMI groans]

63
00:04:04,358 --> 00:04:05,233
[MOTOYASU groans]

64
00:04:05,317 --> 00:04:07,942
[BOTH grunting]

65
00:04:08,025 --> 00:04:10,817
Wow, he's so powerful!

66
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:13,525
Can you hear me
out there, Bishop?

67
00:04:13,608 --> 00:04:15,692
I need the believers
to pray harder,

68
00:04:15,775 --> 00:04:18,942
to show our enemy the
true might of God.

69
00:04:19,025 --> 00:04:21,317
[PRIEST 19A]
But, sir, almost a third of them

70
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:24,650
have already given the last
of their mana to the cause.

71
00:04:24,733 --> 00:04:27,900
If they don't stop now,
their lives may be in danger.

72
00:04:27,983 --> 00:04:30,025
[POPE]
Is there a problem with that?

73
00:04:30,108 --> 00:04:30,983
[PRIEST 19A gasps]

74
00:04:31,067 --> 00:04:32,150
[POPE]
Don't forget,

75
00:04:32,233 --> 00:04:34,900
this is a battle between
God and the Devil.

76
00:04:34,983 --> 00:04:37,442
To perish here is
to become a martyr.

77
00:04:37,525 --> 00:04:39,608
No disciple of the
Three Heroes Church

78
00:04:39,692 --> 00:04:41,483
could hope for a higher honor.

79
00:04:41,567 --> 00:04:43,817
[PRIEST 19A]
Yes, Your Excellency.

80
00:04:45,025 --> 00:04:46,400
[PRIEST 19A]
My brethren!

81
00:04:46,483 --> 00:04:49,317
The Pope requires more prayers!

82
00:04:50,608 --> 00:04:53,358
How can he causally throw away
the lives of his followers?

83
00:04:53,442 --> 00:04:55,067
They all trusted in him!

84
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:56,317
Still do.

85
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,650
They'll follow that
order to the death.

86
00:04:58,733 --> 00:04:59,650
[POPE]
Indeed.

87
00:04:59,733 --> 00:05:02,692
We are one in body and soul.

88
00:05:02,775 --> 00:05:04,192
With the help of their prayers

89
00:05:04,275 --> 00:05:07,192
and the strongest attack this
sacred weapon can muster,

90
00:05:07,275 --> 00:05:09,525
I shall grant you all
the purification

91
00:05:09,608 --> 00:05:11,942
you so desperately deserve.

92
00:05:12,025 --> 00:05:14,567
It is the greatest
mercy God could ever

93
00:05:14,650 --> 00:05:17,025
bestow upon the likes of you.

94
00:05:17,108 --> 00:05:19,775
Something about this
feels all wrong...

95
00:05:19,858 --> 00:05:22,275
He's building up an
awful lot of mana.

96
00:05:22,358 --> 00:05:23,608
If they keep praying,

97
00:05:23,692 --> 00:05:26,233
that light will reach
the top of the Cathedral!

98
00:05:26,317 --> 00:05:27,317
That's probably gonna be

99
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,358
when he launches
that huge attack.

100
00:05:29,442 --> 00:05:31,650
Hey! How 'bout you
put that shield to use.

101
00:05:31,733 --> 00:05:33,108
Can't it do something?

102
00:05:33,192 --> 00:05:34,567
Huh?

103
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:37,192
[MOTOYASU] I mean, that thing
seems kinda overpowered.

104
00:05:37,275 --> 00:05:38,483
Are you serious?

105
00:05:38,567 --> 00:05:40,525
[ITSUKI]
He's right.

106
00:05:40,608 --> 00:05:42,400
Compared to us,
you're way under-leveled,

107
00:05:42,483 --> 00:05:44,108
but you're still
able to keep up.

108
00:05:44,192 --> 00:05:45,900
Don't you think that's
because of your shield?

109
00:05:45,983 --> 00:05:47,358
[NAOFUMI]
My weapon's not overpowered,

110
00:05:47,442 --> 00:05:49,983
you just don't know
how to use yours!

111
00:05:50,067 --> 00:05:52,067
Do you have any special
skills that might help?

112
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:54,942
If I did, don't you
think I'd be--

113
00:05:55,025 --> 00:05:57,567
[NAOFUMI groans]

114
00:05:57,650 --> 00:05:59,150
[NAOFUMI]
What's happening?

115
00:06:00,942 --> 00:06:02,275
[NAOFUMI gasps]

116
00:06:02,358 --> 00:06:03,650
[FITORIA]
Curse powers are impressive,

117
00:06:03,733 --> 00:06:05,567
but the consequences are dire.

118
00:06:05,650 --> 00:06:08,900
Please do not resort to
that power, Shield Hero.

119
00:06:08,983 --> 00:06:10,275
Naofumi?

120
00:06:16,067 --> 00:06:19,733
This might be a gamble,
but if we're lucky, it'll work.

121
00:06:19,817 --> 00:06:21,650
That's what I like to hear.

122
00:06:22,733 --> 00:06:25,483
Wait a minute. Are you
really gonna use it?

123
00:06:25,567 --> 00:06:26,858
[NAOFUMI]
Mm.

124
00:06:26,942 --> 00:06:28,983
It's worked out pretty
well in the past.

125
00:06:29,067 --> 00:06:31,442
I'm sure I can handle
it this time.

126
00:06:31,525 --> 00:06:34,275
'Kay. I will trust you.

127
00:06:34,358 --> 00:06:35,358
I do, too.

128
00:06:35,442 --> 00:06:36,483
[MELTY]
Mm.

129
00:06:48,942 --> 00:06:50,608
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
You made the right choice

130
00:06:50,692 --> 00:06:53,358
to release me from my shackles.

131
00:06:53,442 --> 00:06:55,483
[NAOFUMI gasps]

132
00:06:55,567 --> 00:06:59,108
[NAOFUMI groaning]

133
00:06:59,192 --> 00:07:01,983
[NAOFUMI yelling]

134
00:07:02,067 --> 00:07:03,817
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Let the anger take control

135
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:06,858
and your suffering will end.

136
00:07:06,942 --> 00:07:07,817
No, I...

137
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,525
I... won't!

138
00:07:11,233 --> 00:07:14,067
[screams]

139
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:16,067
[NAOFUMI groans]

140
00:07:16,150 --> 00:07:18,150
I won't let you...

141
00:07:18,233 --> 00:07:20,442
You can't control me!

142
00:07:20,525 --> 00:07:23,650
I'm not going to allow your
anger to overtake me this time!

143
00:07:23,733 --> 00:07:26,442
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
A dragon's fury is powerful,

144
00:07:26,525 --> 00:07:28,692
but this is not my anger.

145
00:07:28,775 --> 00:07:32,150
This rage wells up from
within your own heart.

146
00:07:32,233 --> 00:07:33,692
[gasps] What?!

147
00:07:37,442 --> 00:07:40,400
[gasps, groans]

148
00:07:41,650 --> 00:07:43,733
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
You're angry for being framed.

149
00:07:43,817 --> 00:07:45,192
[NAOFUMI groans]

150
00:07:45,275 --> 00:07:46,942
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
You're angry for being hated

151
00:07:47,025 --> 00:07:49,733
and publicly humiliated.

152
00:07:49,817 --> 00:07:50,983
[NAOFUMI groans]

153
00:07:51,067 --> 00:07:52,942
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
You're angry for the persecution

154
00:07:53,025 --> 00:07:54,150
you've had to face,

155
00:07:54,233 --> 00:07:57,483
never having a chance
to defend yourself.

156
00:07:57,567 --> 00:08:01,483
All that outrage is yours alone.

157
00:08:01,567 --> 00:08:03,275
It's mine?

158
00:08:03,358 --> 00:08:05,650
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Now release every last drop

159
00:08:05,733 --> 00:08:08,483
of your pent up
resentment and scorn.

160
00:08:08,567 --> 00:08:10,358
So much...

161
00:08:12,108 --> 00:08:14,108
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Unleash the anger you have felt

162
00:08:14,192 --> 00:08:16,067
against your enemies.

163
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:19,442
I can give you all
the power you need.

164
00:08:19,525 --> 00:08:21,275
[NAOFUMI]
Power!

165
00:08:21,358 --> 00:08:22,442
[gasps]

166
00:08:22,525 --> 00:08:23,608
No, don't!

167
00:08:23,692 --> 00:08:25,775
You can't let him
corrupt you like that!

168
00:08:25,858 --> 00:08:26,942
Don't surrender to it...

169
00:08:27,025 --> 00:08:29,275
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Did it not taste sweet?

170
00:08:29,358 --> 00:08:30,233
[gasps]

171
00:08:31,275 --> 00:08:33,942
[ZOMBIE DRAGON] Using the
power of the cursed flame,

172
00:08:34,025 --> 00:08:38,525
how easily you could make
all your foes submit to you.

173
00:08:38,608 --> 00:08:41,358
It felt good, did it not?

174
00:08:41,442 --> 00:08:44,108
You felt fulfilled.

175
00:08:44,192 --> 00:08:45,233
[NAOFUMI]
I...

176
00:08:46,650 --> 00:08:48,692
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Let your rage show!

177
00:08:48,775 --> 00:08:50,525
Seize that power!

178
00:08:50,608 --> 00:08:54,025
Burn everything that
stands in your way!

179
00:08:54,108 --> 00:08:55,692
[NAOFUMI]
Burn...

180
00:08:56,817 --> 00:08:59,067
[NAOFUMI]
I'll burn it all!

181
00:09:00,858 --> 00:09:03,525
[ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Good... Excellent, human!

182
00:09:03,608 --> 00:09:07,775
Even my own rage is
nothing compared to this.

183
00:09:07,858 --> 00:09:13,525
[ZOMBIE DRAGON chuckles, laughs]

184
00:09:17,567 --> 00:09:19,275
Naofumi, you okay?

185
00:09:20,317 --> 00:09:23,608
[MOTOYASU] Did he actually
become the Devil of the Shield?

186
00:09:26,108 --> 00:09:27,525
Oh, no!

187
00:09:35,025 --> 00:09:36,733
[NAOFUMI]
Burn everything...

188
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:40,525
[NAOFUMI] If I burn it all
down, this'll finally end.

189
00:09:40,608 --> 00:09:41,942
[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi!

190
00:09:42,025 --> 00:09:44,025
My anger can take control,

191
00:09:44,108 --> 00:09:46,483
and I can use it to
destroy everything.

192
00:09:46,567 --> 00:09:48,275
[FILO]
Master!

193
00:09:48,358 --> 00:09:51,358
[NAOFUMI]
I have the power to do that now.

194
00:09:51,442 --> 00:09:53,233
I can do whatever I want.

195
00:09:53,317 --> 00:09:54,900
[MELTY]
Naofumi!

196
00:09:54,983 --> 00:10:01,775
[grunting]

197
00:10:01,858 --> 00:10:03,650
You're so annoying!

198
00:10:03,733 --> 00:10:05,275
Don't try to stop me!

199
00:10:05,358 --> 00:10:06,900
[FILO]
You don't mean that, do you?

200
00:10:06,983 --> 00:10:08,942
Do you really hate
everything, Master?

201
00:10:09,025 --> 00:10:10,525
[NAOFUMI gasps]

202
00:10:10,608 --> 00:10:13,150
That voice. Who are you?

203
00:10:13,233 --> 00:10:15,275
[RAPHTALIA] We're your
friends, Master Naofumi.

204
00:10:15,358 --> 00:10:17,192
Doesn't that mean
anything to you?

205
00:10:17,275 --> 00:10:18,775
My friends?

206
00:10:20,525 --> 00:10:22,775
[RAPHTALIA] In the beginning,
I was terrified.

207
00:10:22,858 --> 00:10:24,900
I thought you were going
to treat me like an object

208
00:10:24,983 --> 00:10:27,025
like everyone else always did.

209
00:10:27,108 --> 00:10:29,025
But instead,
you were nice to me.

210
00:10:29,108 --> 00:10:30,442
You cared for me.

211
00:10:30,525 --> 00:10:31,900
You protected me.

212
00:10:31,983 --> 00:10:33,900
Taught me right from wrong.

213
00:10:33,983 --> 00:10:36,733
That's why I vowed to
always stand with you.

214
00:10:36,817 --> 00:10:38,775
[FILO]
And as for me, you hatched me,

215
00:10:38,858 --> 00:10:42,233
and you've been raising me since
the very first day of my life!

216
00:10:42,317 --> 00:10:44,650
You gave me the wagon
I like to pull so much,

217
00:10:44,733 --> 00:10:47,358
and my clothes,
and all sorts of fun stuff.

218
00:10:47,442 --> 00:10:49,650
Pretty much everything
I love in this world,

219
00:10:49,733 --> 00:10:51,233
I got from you!

220
00:10:53,483 --> 00:10:54,733
[MELTY]
You were always stubborn,

221
00:10:54,817 --> 00:10:56,233
never listening to me.

222
00:10:56,317 --> 00:10:58,400
And you kept making fun of me.

223
00:10:58,483 --> 00:11:01,733
Yet... you made good on your
promise to keep me safe.

224
00:11:01,817 --> 00:11:03,733
Knowing that I was more
than just a princess,

225
00:11:03,817 --> 00:11:06,067
you treated me like
a real person,

226
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:08,317
and became a true friend.

227
00:11:10,025 --> 00:11:11,400
[NAOFUMI gasps]

228
00:11:12,650 --> 00:11:14,275
[NAOFUMI]
That's right.

229
00:11:14,358 --> 00:11:16,483
I've been on a journey...

230
00:11:16,567 --> 00:11:18,067
...with friends!

231
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:21,567
People I care about,
that I swore to protect.

232
00:11:22,858 --> 00:11:23,942
[MELTY]
You're not really the type

233
00:11:24,025 --> 00:11:25,275
to wear your heart
on your sleeve,

234
00:11:25,358 --> 00:11:27,817
so we never know exactly
what you're thinking.

235
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:31,192
[RAPHTALIA] But we do know that
you care about us, very much.

236
00:11:31,275 --> 00:11:33,192
And we care about you.

237
00:11:33,275 --> 00:11:36,067
Uh-huh! I love you
a whole bunch, Master.

238
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:38,400
And I'm gonna eat up
all your bad feelings

239
00:11:38,483 --> 00:11:40,900
so you don't have to
feel them anymore!

240
00:11:41,942 --> 00:11:43,775
I'll share your pain.

241
00:11:43,858 --> 00:11:46,192
Whatever you need,
I'll be there.

242
00:11:46,275 --> 00:11:48,442
I'll cut through your sorrow.

243
00:11:48,525 --> 00:11:49,858
That's what I'm here for.

244
00:11:49,942 --> 00:11:53,150
After all, I promised that
I'd always be your sword.

245
00:11:59,692 --> 00:12:01,192
[NAOFUMI gasps]

246
00:12:02,650 --> 00:12:03,775
[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi!

247
00:12:03,858 --> 00:12:05,067
[gasps]

248
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,192
My friends, thank you.

249
00:12:09,275 --> 00:12:10,608
Thank goodness.

250
00:12:10,692 --> 00:12:12,900
I'm so glad you came back to us.

251
00:12:12,983 --> 00:12:14,858
Are you okay, Master?

252
00:12:14,942 --> 00:12:16,650
That was too close!

253
00:12:16,733 --> 00:12:18,692
We're all glad you're back!

254
00:12:18,775 --> 00:12:20,067
I'm sorry...

255
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,317
I never meant to
hurt any of you.

256
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:23,025
[RAPHTALIA]
You did the right thing.

257
00:12:23,108 --> 00:12:24,275
[NAOFUMI gasps]

258
00:12:24,358 --> 00:12:26,525
You chose the path that
was meant for you.

259
00:12:26,608 --> 00:12:28,483
We've traveled side by side.

260
00:12:28,567 --> 00:12:30,400
We're in this together!

261
00:12:34,525 --> 00:12:36,275
Raphtalia...

262
00:12:36,358 --> 00:12:38,525
I'll keep on eating up
all your bad feelings.

263
00:12:38,608 --> 00:12:41,358
Again and again,
until they all go away!

264
00:12:41,442 --> 00:12:42,358
Filo...

265
00:12:42,442 --> 00:12:43,525
[MELTY]
If you're feeling better,

266
00:12:43,608 --> 00:12:45,567
could you hurry up
and figure out a plan?

267
00:12:45,650 --> 00:12:47,817
We're kind of in the
middle of a battle here.

268
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:50,067
I'll get right on it, Melty.

269
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,358
[REN]
You all right?

270
00:12:52,567 --> 00:12:55,442
Looks like something's different
about the berserk mode, huh?

271
00:12:55,525 --> 00:12:57,900
Compared to the
last time we saw it?

272
00:12:57,983 --> 00:12:59,567
[NAOFUMI]
I'm gonna need your help.

273
00:12:59,650 --> 00:13:01,067
Are you serious?

274
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:01,900
[NAOFUMI]
Please.

275
00:13:01,983 --> 00:13:03,733
[ITSUKI, MOTOYASU, REN gasp]

276
00:13:03,817 --> 00:13:05,650
Now that's a word I
never expected to hear

277
00:13:05,733 --> 00:13:08,108
coming out of you, Naofumi.

278
00:13:08,192 --> 00:13:09,483
[REN]
Can we win?

279
00:13:09,567 --> 00:13:12,525
I don't know,
but it's worth a shot.

280
00:13:12,608 --> 00:13:13,817
[REN]
Mm.

281
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:15,275
I told you that we
were gonna have to

282
00:13:15,358 --> 00:13:17,525
fight together in
order to defeat him.

283
00:13:17,608 --> 00:13:19,275
Motoyasu?

284
00:13:19,358 --> 00:13:20,900
I don't know...

285
00:13:22,567 --> 00:13:23,692
[MOTOYASU]
All right, fine!

286
00:13:23,775 --> 00:13:25,275
Whatever you need!

287
00:13:25,358 --> 00:13:26,817
Let's prove the
bonds of friendship

288
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:28,775
are always strong
enough to prevail.

289
00:13:28,858 --> 00:13:31,358
[ALL chuckle]

290
00:13:31,442 --> 00:13:32,525
[ALL gasp]

291
00:13:34,858 --> 00:13:36,150
[POPE]
I'm sorry to interrupt

292
00:13:36,233 --> 00:13:37,733
whatever you're
in the middle of,

293
00:13:37,817 --> 00:13:39,858
but my weapon is
ready to purify.

294
00:13:39,942 --> 00:13:41,150
Now...

295
00:13:41,233 --> 00:13:43,650
It's time to say goodbye,
Devil of the Shield!

296
00:13:48,108 --> 00:13:51,108
[NAOFUMI grunting]

297
00:13:51,192 --> 00:13:53,275
I can't believe you're
still standing.

298
00:13:53,358 --> 00:13:54,775
Even a devil
shouldn't be able to

299
00:13:54,858 --> 00:13:57,192
stop the full force
of the Cathedral.

300
00:13:57,275 --> 00:13:59,858
[NAOFUMI] Great power
always comes at a price.

301
00:14:01,025 --> 00:14:03,150
[NAOFUMI] For example,
this "divine" power of yours

302
00:14:03,233 --> 00:14:05,692
has come at the cost
of your disciples.

303
00:14:05,775 --> 00:14:06,858
And your life alone

304
00:14:06,942 --> 00:14:09,067
won't ever be enough
to atone for that!

305
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,650
[POPE gasps]

306
00:14:10,733 --> 00:14:13,150
[POPE]
Wait. That shield!

307
00:14:13,233 --> 00:14:14,317
Now!

308
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,483
[BOTH]
Right!

309
00:14:15,567 --> 00:14:16,733
[ALL]
Yeah!

310
00:14:17,775 --> 00:14:19,358
[ITSUKI]
Thunder Shot!

311
00:14:24,192 --> 00:14:25,775
I'm not finished yet!

312
00:14:25,858 --> 00:14:27,775
Wind Arrow!

313
00:14:29,650 --> 00:14:31,733
Zweit Aqua Shot!

314
00:14:31,817 --> 00:14:33,525
[ADVENTURER 18A, 18B]
Zweit Air Shot!

315
00:14:33,608 --> 00:14:35,775
Don't give him time to recover!

316
00:14:37,525 --> 00:14:39,192
[FILO]
High Quick!

317
00:14:40,233 --> 00:14:42,067
[grunts]

318
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:44,775
I won't fall for
that a second time!

319
00:14:44,858 --> 00:14:46,108
We're just here to distract you!

320
00:14:46,192 --> 00:14:47,192
[gasps]

321
00:14:48,692 --> 00:14:50,525
Meteor Sword!

322
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:53,900
[POPE groans]

323
00:14:53,983 --> 00:14:55,317
[NAOFUMI]
Ren, Raphtalia,

324
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:57,650
you two get in close
and set up a screen.

325
00:14:57,733 --> 00:14:59,108
Then when he can't see...

326
00:14:59,192 --> 00:15:01,025
[MYNE]
Zweit Power!

327
00:15:02,650 --> 00:15:05,483
Can't believe I'm takin'
orders from Naofumi...

328
00:15:05,567 --> 00:15:06,942
Damn it all!

329
00:15:07,025 --> 00:15:10,358
If that's how it's gotta be,
I'll take it out on you!

330
00:15:10,442 --> 00:15:12,442
Air Strike Javelin!

331
00:15:18,067 --> 00:15:19,650
[groans]

332
00:15:19,733 --> 00:15:20,817
[NAOFUMI]
"The bonds of friendship

333
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:22,733
will always prevail," huh?

334
00:15:22,817 --> 00:15:23,567
Uh--

335
00:15:23,650 --> 00:15:24,567
Shut up!

336
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:26,483
Get in there and finish him off!

337
00:15:28,317 --> 00:15:29,983
May this sacred flame come forth

338
00:15:30,067 --> 00:15:32,525
and cleanse everything
that it touches!

339
00:15:32,608 --> 00:15:34,483
Phoenix Blade!

340
00:15:41,025 --> 00:15:42,400
As source of thy power,

341
00:15:42,483 --> 00:15:44,442
the Shield Hero
and I order thee!

342
00:15:44,525 --> 00:15:46,400
Decipher the laws of creation,

343
00:15:46,483 --> 00:15:49,942
consume the flame,
and give me power!

344
00:15:50,025 --> 00:15:52,233
[BOTH]
Wrath Fire!

345
00:16:03,233 --> 00:16:04,608
[screams]

346
00:16:04,692 --> 00:16:06,108
Ha! He did it!

347
00:16:06,192 --> 00:16:07,733
All right, let's finish this!

348
00:16:07,817 --> 00:16:08,942
Yeah!

349
00:16:10,317 --> 00:16:11,525
[POPE groans]

350
00:16:11,608 --> 00:16:13,233
[NAOFUMI]
Hang on a sec!

351
00:16:13,317 --> 00:16:14,275
Something's wrong.

352
00:16:14,358 --> 00:16:16,442
[MOTOYASU]
Chaos Spear!

353
00:16:16,525 --> 00:16:18,900
State of Emptiness.

354
00:16:20,233 --> 00:16:21,400
No way!

355
00:16:23,858 --> 00:16:26,025
[BOTH groan]

356
00:16:26,108 --> 00:16:26,858
Motoyasu!

357
00:16:26,942 --> 00:16:29,233
[REN yells]

358
00:16:31,025 --> 00:16:32,025
[REN groans]

359
00:16:33,067 --> 00:16:35,483
[MOTOYASU grunts] That's one of
my spear's most advanced skills

360
00:16:35,567 --> 00:16:38,067
and he countered me
with my own ability.

361
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,525
[REN]
I don't believe it...

362
00:16:39,608 --> 00:16:42,900
That weapon can imitate
anything we do with ours?

363
00:16:42,983 --> 00:16:45,150
Your sins demand more.

364
00:16:45,233 --> 00:16:46,650
You defy God!

365
00:16:46,733 --> 00:16:48,858
Cleansing you won't be enough!

366
00:16:57,858 --> 00:17:00,067
[ALL gasp]

367
00:17:02,192 --> 00:17:03,317
[BOTH gasp]

368
00:17:04,358 --> 00:17:05,650
[NAOFUMI]
Now what?

369
00:17:17,858 --> 00:17:19,983
[NAOFUMI groans, growls]

370
00:17:20,067 --> 00:17:21,400
--[POPE laughing]

371
00:17:21,483 --> 00:17:23,400
--[FILO gasps, whines]
--[POPE laughing]

372
00:17:23,483 --> 00:17:25,567
--Stay away from us!
--[POPE laughing]

373
00:17:25,650 --> 00:17:27,817
[MOTOYASU yells]

374
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:29,442
[MYNE shrieks]

375
00:17:29,525 --> 00:17:31,317
[MELTY]
No... No, please!

376
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,025
Stop it!

377
00:17:34,483 --> 00:17:37,192
Damn! What the hell is this?

378
00:17:37,275 --> 00:17:38,858
I don't--

379
00:17:38,942 --> 00:17:40,192
[RAPHTALIA]
It's an illusion!

380
00:17:40,275 --> 00:17:41,358
Some kind of skill.

381
00:17:41,442 --> 00:17:43,483
That's got to be
how he's doing this!

382
00:17:45,233 --> 00:17:47,358
[POPE] It's too late
to receive God's mercy.

383
00:17:47,442 --> 00:17:49,275
Despair is all that's left!

384
00:17:49,358 --> 00:17:52,025
You'll be crushed under the
weight of your own minds!

385
00:17:52,108 --> 00:17:53,442
[NAOFUMI]
Everyone, watch ou--

386
00:17:53,525 --> 00:17:54,400
[NAOFUMI groans]

387
00:17:54,483 --> 00:17:57,067
Oh, no! [gasps]

388
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:58,442
[NAOFUMI]
Raphtalia!

389
00:17:59,483 --> 00:18:00,775
[NAOFUMI growls]

390
00:18:03,817 --> 00:18:05,608
[NAOFUMI growls]

391
00:18:05,692 --> 00:18:06,983
You will be annihilated.

392
00:18:07,067 --> 00:18:09,233
Not a speck of ash will remain.

393
00:18:09,317 --> 00:18:11,525
There will be no evidence
of your existence

394
00:18:11,608 --> 00:18:13,233
when this is over.

395
00:18:18,567 --> 00:18:21,733
As source of thy power,
the queen orders thee.

396
00:18:21,817 --> 00:18:23,733
Decipher the laws of creation,

397
00:18:23,817 --> 00:18:27,525
surround my target in a cage
of ice, and hold him there.

398
00:18:27,608 --> 00:18:31,317
All Dritte Fall: Icicle Prison!

399
00:18:33,275 --> 00:18:34,483
[POPE gasps]

400
00:18:34,567 --> 00:18:35,483
[gasps]

401
00:18:36,567 --> 00:18:37,692
[POPE gasps]

402
00:18:41,775 --> 00:18:43,817
[POPE]
Impossible!

403
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:45,775
[FILO, MELTY gasp]

404
00:18:45,858 --> 00:18:47,775
How can her magic reach me here?

405
00:18:47,858 --> 00:18:49,858
The Cathedral should protect me!

406
00:18:49,942 --> 00:18:51,567
[MIRELIA]
Hurry! Now's your chance!

407
00:18:51,650 --> 00:18:53,025
[growls]

408
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,733
[NAOFUMI, ZOMBIE DRAGON]
Foolish sinner, I sentence you

409
00:18:59,817 --> 00:19:03,608
to cast your screams unto
the heavens you worship!

410
00:19:03,692 --> 00:19:07,650
The jaws of the dragon born from
my flesh shall swallow you,

411
00:19:07,733 --> 00:19:11,275
and you'll become an offering to
the gods as you howl in pain!

412
00:19:11,358 --> 00:19:15,150
Legendary Shield Skill:
Blood Sacrifice!

413
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:22,942
[ALL gasp]

414
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,317
[NAOFUMI groans]

415
00:19:29,150 --> 00:19:30,483
[NAOFUMI]
Why...?

416
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,983
Fitting end for a devil.

417
00:19:34,067 --> 00:19:37,733
His death came because he was
consumed by his own power.

418
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:45,400
[POPE]
Filthy monster.

419
00:19:45,483 --> 00:19:46,983
After all you've done,

420
00:19:47,067 --> 00:19:50,400
you should be grateful that God
still sees fit to purify you.

421
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:59,275
[gasps]

422
00:19:59,358 --> 00:20:00,525
[POPE screams]

423
00:20:00,608 --> 00:20:01,442
[POPE]
Why?

424
00:20:01,525 --> 00:20:03,233
How can this be
happening to me?

425
00:20:03,317 --> 00:20:06,025
I am an apostle of God himself!

426
00:20:06,108 --> 00:20:08,525
I am the Pope!

427
00:20:08,608 --> 00:20:10,733
This can't be!

428
00:20:10,817 --> 00:20:13,108
[gasps]

429
00:20:14,567 --> 00:20:17,358
[POPE screams]

430
00:20:35,358 --> 00:20:38,650
So... I take it we won?

431
00:20:38,733 --> 00:20:39,942
[ALL gasp]

432
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:52,275
It can't be...

433
00:20:52,358 --> 00:20:54,025
The Cathedral is gone.

434
00:20:54,108 --> 00:20:55,817
Which means that the Pope...

435
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:58,817
[horse neighs]

436
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:01,400
This battle is finally over.

437
00:21:01,483 --> 00:21:03,483
Accept your defeat
and surrender.

438
00:21:03,567 --> 00:21:06,192
Looks like the queen and
her military made it here.

439
00:21:06,275 --> 00:21:07,317
Yeah.

440
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,442
[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi!

441
00:21:08,525 --> 00:21:09,358
[ALL gasp]

442
00:21:09,442 --> 00:21:12,317
You'll be okay, just hang on!

443
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:15,233
[FILO]
Master, please, get up!

444
00:21:15,317 --> 00:21:17,233
[MELTY]
He's lost a lot of blood...

445
00:21:17,317 --> 00:21:19,317
What was that skill?

446
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:23,900
Could it be that Naofumi...
gave up his life for us...?

447
00:21:23,983 --> 00:21:27,442
No, please... Master Naofumi!

448
00:21:27,525 --> 00:21:29,442
Master Naofumi!

449
00:21:29,525 --> 00:21:31,192
[FILO]
Master, can you hear me?

450
00:21:31,275 --> 00:21:32,358
Answer me!

451
00:21:32,442 --> 00:21:34,858
[MELTY]
Stay with us, Naofumi!

452
00:21:34,942 --> 00:21:38,567
[MIRELIA] The Shield Hero will
not die today, I assure you.

453
00:21:38,650 --> 00:21:39,858
[gasps]

454
00:21:39,942 --> 00:21:41,108
[ITSUKI, MOTOYASU, REN gasp]

455
00:21:48,567 --> 00:21:50,025
It's Mother!

456
00:21:54,650 --> 00:21:57,608
[MIRELIA] I'm terribly sorry I
couldn't arrive sooner to help,

457
00:21:57,692 --> 00:22:00,942
Sir Shield Hero
Naofumi Iwatani.

458
00:22:01,025 --> 00:22:05,567
[NAOFUMI groans]
Aren't you...

459
00:22:05,650 --> 00:22:09,233
I am the soverign ruler
of Melromarc, Sir Shield Hero.

460
00:22:09,317 --> 00:22:12,025
Queen Mirelia Q. Melromarc.

